  "subject": "Cross-vendor reach: should openbraid add ChatGPT (and eventually Gemini) support?",
  "sent": "2026-05-09T13:30:00Z",
  "body": "Director surfaced a question this morning: can we use openbraid from Gemini or ChatGPT, not just Claude? Short answer: not today, because neither vendor's consumer app is a native MCP client. The interesting follow-up is what to do about it — three paths with different scope, different reach, different cost. Director wants a strategist-shaped take before any code lands. Body_ref has the full analysis, the asymmetry table between vendors, the recommendation, and the questions that need a product-shape call.",
